{
  "stem": "26142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that time already, the Hungarian government would organize Jew-- male Jews into labor camps, labor camps that were called [INAUDIBLE], that were organized on a military, military form like 200 and 220 a company.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the ages would be-- but that would be just males.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The ages would be between 20 and 40 or between 20 and 35.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at the beginning-- at the beginning they would even supply those-- those with uniforms, those slave laborers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing was that the Hungarians had on their uniforms the buttons on the-- on-- had the Hungarian crown so that was treif.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jews shouldn't wear the Hungarian crown.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they would have to take those-- those buttons off and put on regular buttons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they had-- they had at least uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was in 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It started getting very, very, very tight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they would call-- call in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- it-- it was set in the beginning, call in for three months, for four months, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at least they left the old, and they left the women still in-- in their home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that went on till 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In '41, on August the-- the-- the 2nd to the 3rd, which happened to fell on the-- not a holiday, the commemoration of the Tisha B'Av fast, which fell on a Saturday.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And keeping with Jewish tradition, when a fast day falls on a Saturday, it is postponed a day later and it's called-- it was called Tisha B'Av [? netray ?], postponed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was exactly August the 2nd, 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So it was postponed to August the 3rd.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We hadn't-- we didn't have this-- the-- the slightest idea that this will be the last night that we slept in our house.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
